data.description: Love at 1st sight is what you'll say when you enter this jaw-dropping, amazing home. You'll be greeted by well-manicured landscaping as you drive up to the entrance. This home features a flex space that can double as an office. The open floor plan is inviting and ready for entertainment. The kitchen boasts beautiful cabinetry topped with granite counters & stainless steel appliances. The primary suite is ginormous which includes 2 walk-in closets, a spa-like bathroom with soaking tub, separate shower, water closet & 2 separate sinks. It doesn't stop there...wait until you see the massively fenced backyard. This yard is ideal when having gatherings for any occasion.GRAYSTONE RESERVE is a sought after neighborhood that is not far from the interstate, shopping and more.  The Only thing this home is missing is YOU! **Seller to contribute towards closing costs**
